Automatically translates your blog in multilanguage by Youdao Translation Engine!

== Description ==

Youdao Translator automatically translates your blog only by moving your mouse in the following four languages pairs:
	Chinese-English
	Chinese-Japanese
	Chinese-Korean
	Chinese-France

Main features:

	*Ripe and popular translation engine: Youdao Translation Engine
	*No database modifications: Youdao Translator is not intrusive. It doesn't create or alter any table on your database, this feature permits to obtain better performances.
	*Be expert in Chinese: It can help you to reach a lot of new users and consequently to strongly increase your popularity, especially your most blogs are Chinese, if you derive some benefits and if you want to support the development, please consider to support me with a donation.

For the latest information and changelog visit the website

http://www.leexiang.com/youdao-translator-plugin

== Installation ==

1. Upload the folder "youdao-translator" to the "wp-content/plugins" directory.
2. Activate the plugin through the 'Plugins' menu in WordPress. 
3. From the main menu choose "Options->Youdao Translator" and set your Youdao Translation API site and key, then select "Update Options".

