== Frequently Asked Questions ==

= How to apply the Youdao Translation API? =

You can visit the website http://fanyi.youdao.com/fanyiapi to apply a key according to your need.

= How to translate your blog when you reading? =

You can choose some words or several sentences using your mouse, then you can see the translation of what you just choose. But notice that you'd better not choose the words whose number is beyond 200.